beer.beer_description: Liberty’s version of the quintessential Kiwi thirst quencher pairs biscuity malts with a good dose of fruity flavour via US hops. But unlike most hoppy heavy hitters, it won’t whack you over the fence for a 6 and out. Making it oh so easy to knock back a couple more before you have to sort the BBQ.
